

Q1. Write a shell script to read name, dept. and basic salary of an employee
    and find the HRD, DA and ,AU

    if BS > 10,000
        HRA = 15% of BS
        DA = 25% of BS
        AU = 5% of BS
    else
        HRA = 13% of BS
        DA = 20% of BS
        AU = 3% of BS

